body.description: Stay organized and prepared for every class with the Oxford College Ruled Spiral Notebook 8.5 X 11 - 1 Subject. This convenient 4-pack bundle ensures you have ample supply for all your note-taking needs throughout the semester.Each notebook measures 8.5 X 11 inches, providing a generous writing space to capture your thoughts, lecture notes, and assignments. The college-ruled pages feature evenly spaced lines, allowing you to neatly organize your ideas while maximizing writing space.Crafted with a durable plastic cover, these notebooks are built to withstand the rigors of everyday use. The sturdy cover protects your notes from spills, tears, and creases, ensuring your important work remains intact and presentable.Inside each notebook, you'll find 100 high-quality sheets of college-ruled paper. The smooth texture of the pages enhances your writing experience, making it a pleasure to jot down your thoughts. The paper resists ink bleeding, preventing smudging and allowing for clean, crisp notes.What sets these notebooks apart is the inclusion of a handy divider pocket folder. The folder features a sturdy construction and allows you to store loose papers, handouts, or even small stationery items like sticky notes or paper clips. Keep everything you need in one convenient place for easy access and organization.Whether you're a student, a professional, or someone who loves to jot down ideas, the Oxford College Ruled Spiral Notebook is a versatile and reliable companion. The 4-pack ensures you have plenty of supply to last you through multiple courses or projects.Order your Oxford College Ruled Spiral Notebook 8.5 X 11 - 1 Subject - College Ruled Paper - Durable Plastic Cover - 100 Sheets With Divider Pocket Folder - 4 Pack today and experience the convenience of a high-quality, well-designed notebook that will help you stay on top of your tasks and excel in your academic or professional endeavors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Equal To If Not Better Than Mead 5 Star
reviews.reviewText: I've been trying out different spiral notebooks and while the 5 Star is the standard good stuff, I really don't see any difference between Mead and Oxford. The Oxford paper is a fraction less smooth which gives pencils a fraction more bite, which is what I want. I think I will stick with the Oxford durable plastic cover notebooks. These notebooks are the workhorses of writers. Cheap, strong and will survive backpacks, totally unpretentious and lets you get to work without worrying about messing up your way overpriced Moleskine.
